<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/wales-office> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Wales Office supports the Welsh Secretary and the Parliamentary Under Secretary of State in promoting the best interests of Wales within a stronger United Kingdom. It ensures Welsh interests are represented at the heart of the UK government and the UK government’s responsibilities are represented in Wales."@en .
